data.description: Explore the possibilities of this spacious 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom single-family home situated in Lincoln's Meadowlane neighborhood. With over 2000 square feet, this residence offers a partially finished basement, providing flexibility for various uses. While the home presents an opportunity for cosmetic enhancements, its spacious layout is filled with promise. The backyard features a workshop/storage building and a covered patio, creating an appealing outdoor retreat. The expansive master suite includes a full master bathroom and abundant his-and-her closet space. Located in the Meadowlane neighborhood, this home provides not just a living space but a community lifestyle, with convenient access to local amenities, schools, and parks. Seize the opportunity to make this Meadowlane gem your own – contact us to schedule a showing and envision the future possibilities of this delightful property.
